  "title": "Xtra Lazy Irish Beef Brisket Stew",
  "description": "A hearty, resinous Irish stew featuring tender beef brisket, perfect for a lazy Sunday. This pescatarian-friendly dish is made with a rich, glassy-jelly broth.",
