  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, whisk together the beef broth, tomato paste, thyme, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrots, potatoes, and celery to the pot.",
    "Add the beef brisket chunks to the pot, making sure they are covered with the broth mixture.",
    "Cover the pot with a lid and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Braise the stew for 3 hours, or until the beef is tender and the vegetables are cooked through.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
